title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 302-2.3 - Partnership-names

N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 302-2.3 - Partnership-names

State Regulations

An individual representative shall not: (a) maintain any partnership except with
another licensed representative and after full disclosure of the partnership
terms to the board; and
(b) practice under an assumed or trade name. Notes
